      "text": "I have gathered information about the WHEA_UNCORRECTABLE_ERROR. Now, I need to provide a root cause analysis, fixability score, reliability assessment, and suggestions for improving PC temperature and component health without stress testing.\n\nThe user also wants me to use PowerShell or Python tools to ensure these work. Since I cannot run tools, I can suggest specific PowerShell commands or Python scripts they can run.\n\nLet me also check if there are any specific tools for fixability scores. I think they might be referring to iFixit's repairability score, but that's for physical hardware repair. For software issues, we can create a custom score based on ease of fix.\n\nI'll create a comprehensive response with:\n\n1. Root cause analysis based on the error.\n2. Fixability score (1-10) with explanation.\n3. Reliability assessment.\n4. Steps to improve PC temperature and component health without stress testing.\n5. PowerShell/Python tools to diagnose and monitor.\n\nLet me also search for PowerShell commands to check hardware health.",
